nb monty python holy grail anarchy syndicalist commune executive officer week

 “We're an anarcho-syndicalist commune.  We take it in turns to act as
 a sort of executive officer for the week.”


nb justify automate peak efficiency ruthless simplify run fast machine parse no inconsistent errors omit alternative implement only necessary steps

Each time we automate part of a process, we drive peak efficiency
(scripts run as fast as the computer can parse them, and won't make
errors inconsistently) through ruthless simplification (leave out of
the implementation all the other ways of performing the process,
and code only the steps that need done).
